detail.name: Vegeta
detail.effect: [On Play] Discard 1 card from your hand : Look at 10 cards from the top of your deck and place up to 1 <Artificial Full Moon> into the Battle Area. Place the rest at the bottom of their owner's deck in a random order.

detail.name: ベジータ
detail.effect: 【登場時】自分の手札1枚を捨てる：自分のデッキの上から10枚を見て、「造りだされた満月」1枚までをバトルエリアに置く。残りをランダムにデッキの下に置く。
